</taxonomicNameLabel>
22. Male abdomen (holotype), upper dorsal, lower ventral view. 23−25. Male genitalia (holotype): 23, ventral view; 24, lateral view; 25, anterior view (internal), fultura superior (arrow). 26−27. Female abdomen (MZSP 14.404). 26, upper dorsal, lower ventral view; 27, tergum and sternum VII and VIII (tergum VIII membranous), sternum VIII (arrow). 28−29. Female genitalia (MZSP 14.404). 28, lateral view; 29, posterior view. Scale bar = 1 mm, except Figs 22 and 26 = 1 cm.
</paragraph>
